title: The Gary Null Show
content:
Today’s guest is Dr. <!--more--> Suzanne Humphries and she is a board certified nephrologist and an internist practicing in Bangor Maine.
After witnessing several of her patients developing kidney failure following last seasons H1N1 and seasonal flu vaccines, she undertook an investigation that alighted her into vaccines’ serious risks.
She now focuses on educating physicans and the public on the truth behind vaccines.
Also, we have Dr Jennifer Craig and she trained as a nurse in the UK before immigrating to Canada and earning a doctorate in medical education.
She has been an associate professor at the University of British Columbia’s School of Medicine and became a homeopathist after retirement.
Jennifer is also the author of “Jabs, Jenner and Juggernauts: A Look at Vaccination” published in 2009.
